::DarkMouse::

She shook a little in her sleep.  She thought she felt someone pick 
her up, but couldn't be sure.  She felt pain flow over her like a 
wave and she groaned slightly and softly in her sleep. 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, JP3884@a... wrote:
>     Tarantulas made his way through the remains of the Cave. 
Paralysis and 
> the others were back at base, but he slipped away. After all, he 
needed to 
> keep busy and he didnt plan on staying under Aracnias claw forever.
>     While looking for remains of bits of computers, he heard the 
voice of 
> Darkmouse, injured and hurt. He walked over to her, looked around 
to see if 
> anyone was watching, and then licked the mech flowing from her 
back. It was 
> delicious...pure ecstacy. 
>     But he did have to get her back to base. He lifted her up and 
started 
> back for base, inhaling her wonderful smell the entire time.
